    • Method Detail

      • preCiteQuestion

        boolean preCiteQuestion(Question aQuestion,
                      StringBuilder citation,
                      List<Attachment> attachments)
        Called before the citation text is generated. Here you can generate your own citation text. It will be returned in the Stringbuilder. The attachments will be returned in the List. The StringBuilder and the List are guaranteed to be not null. If this rule returns true the default citation will be used
        Parameters:
        aQuestion - the question that will be forwarded
        attachments - attachments that should be added to the question
        citation - new citation of the question
        Returns:
        true if the default quote will be generated, false the quote is taken from the function

      • postCiteQuestion

        void postCiteQuestion(Question oldQuestion,
                    Question forwardedQuestion)
        Called after the citation text is generated. Here You can make any changes on the copy of the forwarded Questions
        Parameters:
        aQuestion - the question before a text has been changed
        forwardedQuestion - the question after a text has been changed
